Title: OhZee Creative Framework
Description: OhZee Creative Framework contains the base classes used by various applications by OhZee Creative, LLC. Most notably, it's used by OhZee Creative Controls.
HomeWiki:
Project Description
This is the framework that's currently used by OhZee Creative Controls.

Install via NuGet: http://www.nuget.org/packages/OzFramework/

Use at your own risk. Updates to this project may or may not happen.
